sequenceDiagram
    participant Client as Client<br/>(caikit-tgis-serving)
    participant Router as TGIS Router<br/>8033/TCP gRPC<br/>3000/TCP HTTP
    participant Shard0 as Model Shard 0<br/>UDS gRPC<br/>PyTorch
    participant ShardN as Model Shards 1..N<br/>NCCL 29500/TCP
    participant Storage as Model Storage<br/>(PVC/S3)
    participant Kubelet as Kubelet

    Note over Shard0,Storage: Startup: Model Loading
    Shard0->>Storage: Load model weights<br/>(filesystem mount)
    Storage-->>Shard0: Model artifacts

    Note over Client,ShardN: Flow 1: Unary Text Generation (Generate)
    Client->>Router: gRPC Generate<br/>8033/TCP<br/>Optional TLS/mTLS
    Router->>Router: Validate + Tokenize<br/>(in-process)
    Router->>Router: Batch/Queue<br/>(continuous batching)
    Router->>Shard0: Prefill batch<br/>UDS gRPC (plaintext)
    Shard0->>ShardN: Tensor parallel forward<br/>NCCL 29500/TCP (plaintext)
    ShardN-->>Shard0: Partial results
    loop NextToken (autoregressive)
        Router->>Shard0: NextToken<br/>UDS gRPC
        Shard0->>ShardN: NCCL allreduce
        ShardN-->>Shard0: Partial results
        Shard0-->>Router: Generated token(s)
    end
    Router-->>Client: GenerationResponse<br/>gRPC 8033/TCP

    Note over Client,ShardN: Flow 2: Streaming Text Generation (GenerateStream)
    Client->>Router: gRPC GenerateStream<br/>8033/TCP server-streaming<br/>Optional TLS/mTLS
    Router->>Shard0: Prefill + NextToken<br/>UDS gRPC
    Shard0->>ShardN: Tensor parallel<br/>NCCL
    loop Token-by-token streaming
        Shard0-->>Router: Next token
        Router-->>Client: stream GenerationResponse
    end
    Router-->>Client: Stream complete

    Note over Kubelet,Router: Flow 3: Health Check
    Kubelet->>Router: GET /health<br/>HTTP 3000/TCP (plaintext)
    Router-->>Kubelet: 200 OK / 503
